    <section id="about" class="container content-section">
        <section class="about-section">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2"  style="/*border:1px solid #fff;*/ padding: 10px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.75); ">
                <h2>RIT Bikeshare</h2>
                <p>The RIT Bikeshare is a free program to all students enroled and all facuality at RIT.</p>
                <p>You can rent a bike for 24 hours to do what ever you want. Ride around campus, to the Marketplace Mall, or show off your skills to friends.</p>
                <p>More stuff here about how cool it is to rent bikes</p>
                <p>More stuff here about how cool it is to rent bikes</p>
